  "title": "Wholesale Food Trading - Sales Executive (Woodlands)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Develop targeted sales plans</p></li><li><p>Monitor market trends, channels, and competitors</p></li><li><p>Identify performance gaps & propose improvements</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Build leads and networks</p></li><li><p>Drive new customer acquisition</p></li><li><p>Enhance customer retention strategies</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Understand customer needs & present proposals</p></li><li><p>Resolve customer issues</p></li><li><p>Follow up on deals and ensure payment</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Develop CRM programs</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Diploma/Degree in Business or related field</p></li><li><p><strong>Preferrable in </strong>B2B sales experience</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Strong sales planning & methodology</p></li><li><p>Competitor, market & channel analysis</p></li><li><p>Sales performance tracking & reporting</p></li><li><p>CRM proficiency</p></li><li><p>Budget planning & management</p></li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the above positions, please click \"Apply now\" </p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. </p><p>JAC Recruitment Pte. Ltd. </p><p>EA License No: 90C3026</p><p>EA Personnel No: R23113652</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Wong Yi Lei</p>",
